PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN NUNAVUT (THE EEYOU MARINE REGION, NUNAVUT) - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal of some 850 square kilometres of land in order to facilitate the settlement of the Crees of Quebec within the Eeyou Marine Region.
